{"tid":2245453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中五男生被控藏伸縮棍　辯方指控方違不檢控承諾　申永久擱置聆訊","createTime":"2020-10-16T08:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T09:37:14.000Z","uid":365024,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"87576185ad7bce40a59169ad6b61ce643b80f7a8","tid":2245453,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:35:02.000Z","msg":"17 歲中五男學生被指去年 12 月，在大圍藏有一枝伸縮棍，被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪。案件早前提堂時，署理主任裁判官溫紹明提及另一宗相同控罪案件，即中大<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">內地生在校內畢業禮期間，向遊行同學揮刀，該案獲律政司撤銷控罪。溫官明言：「中大揮刀嗰個係大學生，律政司都認為可以放佢一馬；我就覺得呢單案，更多原因值得放」</span></span>，促控辯雙方積極商討處理方式。<br />\n<br />\n控方堅持提告，今（16 日）準備聽取答辯，辯方則向法庭申請永久擱置聆訊，指控方有違不檢控的承諾。裁判官就辯方申請，將案件押至 12 月 1 日審理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%94%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%97%8F%E4%BC%B8%E7%B8%AE%E6%A3%8D-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E9%81%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE-%E7%94%B3%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E6%93%B1%E7%BD%AE%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A/?fbclid=IwAR3mnnwnx8hQ0Y6CHipM9pPKklEcbASCpAXrMkwh6btJC0_TZDjkvC4cUCg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%2594%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E4%25BC%25B8%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E6%25A3%258D-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%2581%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AB%25BE-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E4%25B9%2585%25E6%2593%25B1%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3mnnwnx8hQ0Y6CHipM9pPKklEcbASCpAXrMkwh6btJC0_TZDjkvC4cUCg&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=f5b85843\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%2594%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E4%25BC%25B8%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E6%25A3%258D-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%